			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4624709">
									

<p>Combinations of the six base classes are allowed, but you may only combine two classes and they cannot be two classes simultaneously. &quot;Safe (Formerly Keter)&quot; or &quot;<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">Euclid</span> Neutralized&quot; are allowed, but &quot;Keter/Thaumiel&quot; and &quot;<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">Safe</span> <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">Euclid</span> <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">Keter</span>&quot; are not.</p>

